Rams, has shown no ill effects from the two operations on his left knee. 
</P>
<P>
 "It's the knee where they took the tendon out to repair the other knee," 
Miller said. "I plant on my right leg and I must have been coming across my 
body in a different way because it was tender. As a result, I did something to 
my abdominal muscle and it's just a little sore." 
</P>
