 In what many consider an unprecedented move, Knox invited a reporter who 
regularly covers the Rams to speak to the team this week. 
</P>
<P>
 "I thought it was good -- it's a step in the right direction," Knox said. "The 
media is a very large and important part of pro football." T.J. SIMERS 
