Republican leader Bob Dole or President Clinton? Dole: 34% Clinton: 37% 
Neither/Both: 12% Don't know: 17% * 
</P>
<P>
 Foreign affairs 
</P>
<P>
 Would you favor or oppose the use of U.S. troops, as part of a U.N.-sponsored 
multi-national invasion force, to help restore Haiti's democratically elected 
government? Favor: 36% Oppose: 48% Don't know: 16% * 
</P>
<P>
 Do you think the United State's response to the situation in Rwanda is 
adequate? Adequate: 50% Do more: 26% Done too much: 19% Don't know: 5% Morals, 
Religion and Politics 
</P>
<P>
