 Thousand Oaks will sponsor an art and photography show this fall to celebrate 
the city's 30th anniversary. 
</P>
<P>
 Members of the arts community, including art teacher Joseph A. Gatto of Los 
Angeles, will serve as judges for the show. 
</P>
