</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA072894-0345 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 064928 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
July 28, 1994, Thursday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 6; Column 1; Financial Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
