<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Record label -- In last week's cover story on Arthur Lee and Love, the record 
company that put out Lee's "Girl on Fire" vinyl 45 was incorrectly identified. 
The label is Distortions Records. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Correction 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
